cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this cookbook in teaching or research, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "The LLM Systems Cookbook"
abstract: >-
  A hands-on curriculum for modern LLM systems engineering. 61 Jupyter notebooks covering
  inference, retrieval-augmented generation, training, agents, serving, evaluation, and GPU
  programming, each reimplementing a core technique from first principles, comparing against
  a production tool, and self-scoring with numerical checks.
